  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Taxation and development</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This research will help to address major operational evidence gaps on how to make tax systems more equitable, efficient and conducive to poverty reduction, stable economic growth, and better governance. The supplier will work closely with tax specialists and tax administrations in sub-Saharan Africa and South Asia to i) deliver a high quality set of research findings, ii)  build tax research capacity in low income countries, and iii) engage with policy makers, including HMG, and other stakeholders, to facilitate the uptake and impact of this new research</narrative>
  </description>
